	// recommended action is being applied on the user database. Verifying -> recommended action was applied and is being verified
	// of its usefulness by the system. Success -> recommended action was applied and improvement found during verification. Pending
	// Revert -> verification found little or no improvement so recommended action is queued for revert or user has manually reverted.
	// Reverting -> changes made while applying recommended action are being reverted on the user database. Reverted -> successfully
	// reverted the changes made by recommended action on user database. Ignored -> user explicitly ignored/discarded the recommended
	// action.
